item.description: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection') vulnerability in Contact Form - WPManageNinja LLC Contact Form Plugin – Fastest Contact Form Builder Plugin for WordPress by Fluent Forms fluentform allows SQL Injection.This issue affects Contact Form Plugin – Fastest Contact Form Builder Plugin for WordPress by Fluent Forms: from n/a through 4.3.25.
